msgid ""
"Additional templates may be installed directly, or downloaded from <ulink "
"url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink> by clicking the "
"<guilabel>Download</guilabel> button. Any templates installed by the user "
"may also be deleted. Entry templates are saved in <filename class=\"directory"
"\">~/.local/share/tellico/entry-templates/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Lisamalle saab paigaldada kas käsitsi või laadida alla aadressilt  <ulink "
"url=\"http://kde-files.org/index.php?amp;xcontentmode=676\">kde-files.org</"
"ulink>, milleks tuleb klõpsata nupule <guilabel>Laadi alla</guilabel>. Kõiki "
"kasutaja paigaldatud malle saab ka kustutada. Kirjemallid salvestatakse "
"kataloogi <filename class=\"directory\">$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/apps/"
"tellico/entry-templates/</filename>."

